<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section xml:id="sec-lab-infrared-interaction" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Lab: Infrared Interaction</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>In this lab we'll learn how to use the infrared sensors and emitters to detect objects and their distance, as well as interact with a remote control.</p>
  </introduction>
  <subsection xml:id="subsec-infrared-navigation">
    <title>Infrared Navigation</title>
    <p>Follow along with the <url href="https://learn.parallax.com/courses/infrared-light-navigation-for-the-cyberbot/">Infrared light navigation for the cyber:bot</url> tutorial.</p>
    
  </subsection>
  <subsection xml:id="subsec-infrared-remote-control">
    <title>Infrared Remote Control</title>
    <p>Follow along with the <url href="https://learn.parallax.com/courses/control-your-cyberbot-with-an-infrared-tv-remote/">Control your cyber:bot with an Infrared TV Remote</url> tutorial.</p>
  </subsection>
</section>
